{"tid":2416732,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"AV女優紗倉真菜做性專家 上稻垣吾郎NHK節目談性教育","createTime":"2021-02-21T09:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T15:10:55.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3da9336f64bf1d6ecd17a47c7a74e93cdfcae3ec","tid":2416732,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T09:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1aNjmW5QOarhM06kgiqvE4DcLDU=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2DQJFVM6UNEVFOA4KGS3LU4N7I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1aNjmW5QOarhM06kgiqvE4DcLDU%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2DQJFVM6UNEVFOA4KGS3LU4N7I.jpg&h=c2809339&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報稱27歲的日本AV女優紗倉真菜，獲邀亮相稻垣吾郎主持的NHK電視台深夜節目《不可避研究中》，兩人把不少人難以啟齒的「性教育」話題搬上枱對談研究。<br />\n<br />\n由於國營電視台NHK向來傳統保守，紗倉真菜打破慣例上該台節目，也被視為是突破禁忌，向前邁進一大步。出道10年的紗倉真菜，平時多以性感造型示人，她在IG公開參加該節目的照片，全身卻包到冚，沒在鏡頭前露肉。紗倉真菜留言表示：「學習性教育很丟臉嗎？還是對此一無所知才該慚愧呢？家人又該如何和青春期的孩子討論？」強調性教育的重要性。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pfyVzcDLXASWpqcXtH0vnEdmsD4=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IUG42TDNEVC5LHMZZRBFQUSYOA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpfyVzcDLXASWpqcXtH0vnEdmsD4%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIUG42TDNEVC5LHMZZRBFQUSYOA.jpg&h=ecaaa901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EwDdijPvXrPlikTuYpC2I2hkWNk=/802x878/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EDIE6I4SBVFQLKK5L7WRIAOYBI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEwDdijPvXrPlikTuYpC2I2hkWNk%3D%2F802x878%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEDIE6I4SBVFQLKK5L7WRIAOYBI.JPG&h=747650e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210221/PP2LHYAUZ5CIFNGUQF5EF4OSQE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210221%2FPP2LHYAUZ5CIFNGUQF5EF4OSQE%2F&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=579bc528\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210221%2FPP2LHYAUZ5CIFNGUQF5EF4OSQE%2F&h=7db77427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210221/PP2LHYAUZ5CIFNGUQF5EF4OSQE/</a>"},{"pid":"3ee895b80cd389e344ce13d08d56e307b14cfeb1","tid":2416732,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T09:50:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f45eb34d6992c0cad4fc5551d4a2c5200402fd1","tid":2416732,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T10:01:41.000Z","msg":"真係估唔到 NHK 會有呢種節目 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3d8e087294198ba6cc46695e3586abe006d6d2","tid":2416732,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T10:01:47.000Z","msg":"佢係咪出書個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hk